<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-20-1191 </DOCNO><TEXT>This book discusses the papers presented at the conference of rock mechanics.The topics discussed are: coal mines design; stress control methods,reservoir rocks of coal and petroleum and mining technology; surfaceand underground mining; oil shales and oil sands fracture formations;engineering of rocks; technology of drilling boreholes and productionof oil wells, and radioactive waste disposal with underground miningof rock caverns and salt caverns.</TEXT></DOC>